<div class='container'>
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <h2 class="text-center display-5 py-5" style="background-color:#370F8C; color:white;">GREAT JOB!<br>Now give feedback to your pal ðŸ˜Ž</h2>
      <div class="d-flex flex-direction: column">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1613963931023-5dc59437c8a6?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1738&q=80" alt="We hear you" width="750" height="350">
        <p class="text-center my-3">Just take some time to think back to the details of your call and be honest.<br>It will help your pal a lot!<br>
          We all want to nail that job interview and... make our mum proud!
        </p>
      </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
    <div class="bg-white px-5 py-3 my-5 rounded border border-1 text-center">
      <%= simple_form_for [@videocall, @feedback] do |f| %>
      <div class='my-3'>
        <p>What was your overall impression?</p>
        <div class="rating justify-content-end">
          <% (1..5).to_a.reverse.each do |i| %>
            <%= f.radio_button :overall_impression, i, id: "rating_#{i}", value: "#{i}" %>
            <label for=<%= "rating_#{i}" %>>
              <div class="align-items-center"><i class="fas fa-star" style="direction: ltr;"></i></div>
            </label>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class='my-3'>
          <p>Did your pal make eye-contact with you?</p>
        <div class="rating justify-content-end">
          <% (1..5).to_a.reverse.each do |i| %>
            <%= f.radio_button :eye_contact, i, id: "rating_#{i}", value: "#{i}" %>
            <label for=<%= "rating_#{i}" %>>
              <i class="fas fa-star" style="direction: ltr;"></i>
            </label>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class='my-3'>
          <p>How well was their background presented?</p>
        <div class="rating justify-content-end">
          <% (1..5).to_a.reverse.each do |i| %>
            <%= f.radio_button :background_presentation, i, id: "rating_#{i}", value: "#{i}" %>
            <label for=<%= "rating_#{i}" %>>
              <i class="fas fa-star" style="direction: ltr;"></i>
            </label>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class='my-3'>
          <p>Please assess your pal's problem solving skills</p>
        <div class="rating justify-content-end">
          <% (1..5).to_a.reverse.each do |i| %>
            <%= f.radio_button :problem_solving, i, id: "rating_#{i}", value: "#{i}" %>
            <label for=<%= "rating_#{i}" %>>
              <i class="fas fa-star" style="direction: ltr;"></i>
            </label>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class='my-3'>
          <p>How good was their verbal communication?</p>
        <div class="rating justify-content-end">
          <% (1..5).to_a.reverse.each do |i| %>
            <%= f.radio_button :verbal_communication, i, id: "rating_#{i}", value: "#{i}" %>
            <label for=<%= "rating_#{i}" %>>
              <i class="fas fa-star" style="direction: ltr;"></i>
            </label>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class='my-3'>
          <p>What about body language?</p>
        <div class="rating justify-content-end">
          <% (1..5).to_a.reverse.each do |i| %>
            <%= f.radio_button :body_language, i, id: "rating_#{i}", value: "#{i}" %>
            <label for=<%= "rating_#{i}" %>>
              <i class="fas fa-star" style="direction: ltr;"></i>
            </label>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class='my-3'>
          <p>Did they show enthusiasm during the call?</p>
        <div class="rating justify-content-end">
          <% (1..5).to_a.reverse.each do |i| %>
            <%= f.radio_button :enthusiasm, i, id: "rating_#{i}", value: "#{i}" %>
            <label for=<%= "rating_#{i}" %>>
              <i class="fas fa-star" style="direction: ltr;"></i>
            </label>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class='my-3'>
          <p>Please assess your pal's professional appearance</p>
          <div class="rating justify-content-end">
            <% (1..5).to_a.reverse.each do |i| %>
              <%= f.radio_button :professional_appearance, i, id: "rating_#{i}", value: "#{i}" %>
              <label for=<%= "rating_#{i}" %>>
                <i class="fas fa-star" style="direction: ltr;"></i>
              </label>
            <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class='my-3'>
          <p>Did your pal seem confident?</p>
          <div class="rating justify-content-end">
            <% (1..5).to_a.reverse.each do |i| %>
              <%= f.radio_button :confidence, i, id: "rating_#{i}", value: "#{i}" %>
              <label for=<%= "rating_#{i}" %>>
                <i class="fas fa-star" style="direction: ltr;"></i>
              </label>
            <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class='my-3'>
          <p>Would you actually hire them?</p>
          <div class="rating justify-content-end">
            <% (1..5).to_a.reverse.each do |i| %>
              <%= f.radio_button :hireability, i, id: "rating_#{i}", value: "#{i}" %>
              <label for=<%= "rating_#{i}" %>>
                <i class="fas fa-star" style="direction: ltr;"></i>
              </label>
            <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>






    <%= f.input :written_feedback, label: "Please add here anything that could help them improve even more" %>
    <%= f.submit %>
  <% end %>
</div>
